title: Is this a picture of Piden with Tara Reid?
subtitle: Tara Reid, who served as an assistant to assist in the management of interns to the Biden Senate office in 1993, made an allegation of sexual abuse of the former Vice-President.
author: David Mikkelson
vclaim: A photo showing Joe Biden with Tara Reed, a woman Paden claims to have never met, who accused him of sexual assault.
